# Sparsity Specialized rANS Compression (SSrANS)

This directory contains the SSrANS test and benchmarking code.

### `ratio_comparison.py`
Implements SSrANS, vanilla rANS and bitmap compression algorithms for sparse data, and compares compression ratios at varying sparsity values. Run with `--plot` to create a plot of compression ratio vs sparsity. 

### `benchmark.py`
Implements SSrANS, vanilla rANS and bitmap compression algorithms for sparse data as JAX kernels, with a benchmark harness that reports speed in mega-symbols/s. Useful for TPU speed demonstration.
